content:
You have probably noticed that the website got a HUGE update.
Well, I switched to using the PaperMod theme.
You can still view the old posts, as I had archived them.
The main reason to do this was so I could use Org Mode1, which ox-hugo2 uses PaperMod3 as a template for it. PaperMod3 looks way nicer than the theme I used before.
Since I currently am using the Tokyo Night4 theme, I might update the CSS of the website to have the Tokyo Night4 theme as the website theme.
Hopefully this new style for the website makes it look more modern, instead of looking like a website from the 2000s.
